}

  (* Then *)

  If a_9 = 1
  Then {

        Let m = Mint_2[shift_sint32(queue_0, x_7) <- i_1][a_10 <- 1].

  (* Then *)
  Have: i_1 < n.
  If a_9 = 1
  Then {
    Have: (rear_3 = rear_5) /\ (a_8 = Mint_1).
    If Mint_1[a_10] = 0
    Then {
      Have: rear_5 = rear_2.
      If rear_2 < n
      Then {
        Let x_8 = 1 + rear_1.
        Let m = Mint_1[shift_sint32(queue_0, x_8) <- i_1][a_10 <- 1].
        Have: rear_2 = rear_1.
        Have: x_8 = rear_0.
        Have: m[shift_sint32(dist_0, i_1) <- 1 + m[a_7]] = Mint_0.

    }
    Else { Have: (Mint_1 = Mint_0) /\ (rear_5 = rear_0). }
  }

    (Mint_0
       [shift_sint32(Mptr_0
                       [shift_PTR(graph_0,
                          Mint_0[shift_sint32(queue_0, i_2)])], i)] = 1) /\
    (0 <= i_2) /\ (i_2 < front_0).
